{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I guess the inhabitants of Mauritius tried to put it on the Jews [LAUGHS] and that they didn't have enough to eat-- not on the Jews, on the camp-- that we didn't have enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that changed again after two, three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was sort of understandable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the natives, actually at the beginning were really very, very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Later on, I think they got a little not so nice anymore, because they felt we were taking some food away from them and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was also understandable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But basically, nobody did anything bad really to any of us and most people were reasonably friendly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were about I believe 12 Palestine police with us in the camp, 9 women and-- no, it must have been more, maybe 15.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were about-- there were 5 men and-- now 14-- 5 men and 9 women who were with us all the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And most of them were reasonably nice, except for the commander, who was really very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All in all, life in the camp was not easy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We-- I was very lucky to manage to get into a hut which had a division.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one part of the hut was slated for five people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I happened to be in this particular area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that was much more pleasant than being in a hut with 32 other people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were pretty crowded in that space.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember we-- we counted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had one locker, one bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the whole area was seven planks, you know, of the wooden floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So that was sort of our home for almost five years.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
